 properly recognized and new economic institutions are developed that will encourage people to take care of their landscapes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aAgriculturexEconomic aspects. 0aAgriculturexEnvironmental aspects. 0aAgriculturexSocial aspects. 0aCommunism and agriculture. 7aNATURE / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077356571540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773565715423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773565715/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles